campfires and movie theaters.\n\n--- Coming Soon ---\n\nVIDEO PLAYER: play local video files stored on your VR headset, or stream from a video server.", "short_description": "WATCH movies with friends in a virtual movie theater. \nPLAY your favorite PC video games on a huge screen. \nHANG OUT in social VR chat rooms.\nEVENTS like weekly 3D Movie Nights and VR LAN parties!"}]}, "developer_name": "Bigscreen, Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://bigscreenvr.com/privacypolicy.txt", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://bigscreenvr.com/termsofservice.txt", "publisher_name": "Bigscreen, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://bigscreenvr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["MOVIE", "UTILITY", "SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "en_GB", "en_AU", "en_CA", "en_US", "en_ZA"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "482425683281657"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1111131355761762"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1111131355761762"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1557776927, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1111131355761762"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "26437722252542184", "version": "0.933.55.26a859-beta-creative-beta"}, "id": "405783720195874", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false,